nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: A studio photograph showcases an intriguing subject: an android woman adorned with striking long dreadlocks cascading down her back. The setting is sleek and modern, emphasizing the futuristic, metallic features that distinguish her from a human counterpart. Her expression is stoic yet engaging, as she gazes directly at the camera lens. The photograph highlights details such as the precision of her mechanical joints, the gleam of her synthetic skin, and the intricate design of her dreadlock extensions. The image exudes an air of mystery, merging a human touch with cutting-edge technology in a thought-provoking manner.

Custom Node needs:

Comfyui_three_js, essentials, was-nod-suite-comfyui, rgthree-comfy, MileHighStyler, cg-use-everywhere, x-flux-comfyui, logicUtils, KJNodes
